    <div id="comment_43318745">
        <header data-points="-1" data-reason="Normal">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Please understand THIS IS NOT ME... apk"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Please understand THIS IS NOT ME... apk<span> (-1)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><span class="author" title="author name and user ID">Anonymous Coward</span> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3598019&cid=43318745">(#43318745)</a></h4>
