    <div id="comment_43318693">
        <header data-points="4" data-reason="Insightful">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="The distasteful word."><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>The distasteful word.<span> (4, Insightful)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~neoshroom" class="author" title="author name and user ID">neoshroom (324937) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3598019&cid=43318693">(#43318693)</a></h4>
        </header>
        <div id="comment_body_43318693" class="comment-wrapper" data-points="4" data-reason="Insightful">
