You see, the Leftist narrative is that Muslims commit jihad against the West are forced into extreme measures because they are poor, downtrodden, poorly educated etc. That fits in with the Leftists notions of "huddled masses" they they must fight to free. The reality is that the jihadis that attack the West are usually better educated, monied and privileged than their peers. What is driving them is Islam. The media's narrative is that these are "extremists". In on sense it is true, most Muslims are good people and do not do jihad (thank the FSM), but on the other hand this is a complete lie - the interpretation that the jihadis are taking is not extreme in any way, it is the *mainstream* interpretation of Islam that all four Sunni schools of jurisprudence, the Sunni school and people like Osama bin Laden all agree on. All faithful Muslims agree that jihad is a duty of every devout Muslim, it is just that most don't practice it (often they simply send money to the more vigorous guys).
</p><p>
This sounds bizarre when you first hear it. But it turns out this is the truth about Islam (so please, don't shoot the messenger, me for telling the truth).  What is interesting is not that Islamists are obfuscating their anti-liberty aims, but that the political Left and academia are aiding and abetting them. They use character assassination to try and silence anyone telling the truth (eg. see the recent book documenting this: <a href="http://frontpagemag.com/2013/jamie-glazov/bullies-how-the-lefts-culture-of-fear-and-intimidation-silences-america/" title="frontpagemag.com">http://frontpagemag.com/2013/jamie-glazov/bullies-how-the-lefts-culture-of-fear-and-intimidation-silences-america/</a> <span class="domain-text"> [frontpagemag.com]</span> ).  Isn't it interesting how news and spin is being used to generate a perception that counters the reality of the facts?
</p><p>
I do have one positive thing to say about the Obama Administration. After the disaster in Benghazi (although why have none of the 30 survivors been able to speak freely?) I think the Administration has started to realise that the Muslim Brotherhood advisors in the White House have been giving bad advice and as a result the US has been harming liberty rather than helping it. I think the Administration finally realise that they can't be nice to jihadis (eg. like the ones they were arming in Libya, before they slipped the leash of the US) and expect a measure of control. The Administration has woken up and now opposes arming the Syrian Opposition in Syria. While the US still wants Assad out (he's a bad tyrant) they will not provide dangerous heavy weaponry any more (some of it has already ended up in the hands of the Al Nusra outfits; which are basically Al Qaeda).
</p><p>
So you must ask yourself, irrespective of your political views, why aren't my elected representatives and mainstream media telling me this? Why are they *actively* suppressing the truth: eg.
</p><p>
ps: don't believe the Muslim Brotherhood are influencing the White House? Here's my evidence:<br>
<a href="http://www.investigativeproject.org/3869/egyptian-magazine-muslim-brotherhood-infiltrates" title="investigativeproject.org">http://www.investigativeproject.org/3869/egyptian-magazine-muslim-brotherhood-infiltrates</a> <span class="domain-text"> [investigativeproject.org]</span>  <br>
<br>
Now Senator Michelle Bachmann may be a wierdo, but when she called for an investigation of the MB in the White House it was amazing that only five senators backed her. Surely an investigation would clear everyone so would be no big deal, right? Note that during the Cold War no one opposed investigation of Lefist/Marxist penetration into Government (and after the Cold War it was found to be much deeper than wider than anyone suspected).
</p><p>
Anyway, so now you have some clues about the "Innocence of Muslims". The Islamists pointed the video (that had been out for months with a measly 17 views) to the hordes a few days before the 10th anniversary of 9/11. The crowds go crazy and attack several embassies. The embassy in Benghazi is stormed and the ambassador sodomized and killed. The Obama Administration lies about the events that lead to four dead Americans (an ambassador and courageous SEALs) because they had been running guns to jihadis (who they hoped to control, but couldn't). The Obama Administration had to lie about what they were doing so they blamed a video. In essense they shut down Free Speech of criticism of Islam (which was, when the facts were checked, entirely consistent with Islamic scripture - and because the life of Mohammed was so *evil* Muslims don't want you to know it).  The manufactured "Days of Rage" have been working quite well for the Islamists. They are slowly setting bounds on Free Speech (eg. no criticism of Islam or evil Mohammed is permitted; even if perfectly factual and true). The Obama Administration were compromised enough that they ended up opposing Free Speech (just as the incompetent Secretary of State Hiliary Clinton shamefully co-sponsored the anti-Free Speech UN Resolution 16/18 when she promised to "name and shame" US citizens exercising their First Amendment Rights on US soil !!?).
</p><p>
Sorry for the long post. It was required since the claims I make about the Obama Administration seem implausible (due to the hiding of information) until you put a lot of pieces together and tie it up with what we see going on around the World.  What is happening is not accidental nor random. There is a pattern you will see once you know what to look for. Islam is on the march and it attempting to change Western culture to be more Sharia compliant - and the media, academics, Leftists and ignorant political elites are letting it happen. Fortunately, the sensible common man is starting to wake up, and saying "we won't compromise on liberty". We don't have to get violent to win, we just have to let others know the Truth of what is going on, show the lies of the Islamists and their Leftist allies, and loudly call for the preservation of liberties like Free Speech, Freedom on Conscience, equality for women, equality of all races, oppose anti-Semitism and those that would discriminate against other faiths (eg. the disgusting Islamic ideology of "dhimmis" and "jizya"; basically a Mafia protection racket sanctioned by Islam).
</p></div>
